name: MartialartsDrilloftheday
0: ”Alexa open martial arts drill of the day”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: martial arts drill of the day
des:
Ask for martial arts drills to get a new idea for class. 

Martial arts drill of the day provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you better at martial arts.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch martial arts drill of the day" or "Alexa, open martial arts drill of the day" to get a new drill".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
